3:T788,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is sabji billing software?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Sabji billing software is a purpose-built billing and accounting tool for sabzi mandi traders, vegetable commission agents, and fruit & vegetable wholesalers. Unlike general billing tools, it handles lots, crates, weight, sabji varieties, hamali, palledari, and mandi khata natively — exactly the way traders work at the mandi gate every day."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How fast can I generate a sabji bill in MandiGrow?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"MandiGrow generates a complete GST-compliant sabji sale bill in under 10 seconds. Enter the sabji variety, lot, weight, and rate — commission, hamali, palledari, and market fee are auto-calculated and the digital patti is ready instantly."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does MandiGrow sabji billing software work in Hindi?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. MandiGrow generates bills, pattis, and reports in Hindi, Telugu, Kannada, Tamil, Malayalam, Marathi, and English. Switch language with one tap. Your sabji buyers and farmers can receive bills in their preferred language."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can MandiGrow sabji billing software work offline?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. MandiGrow works on Android mobile phones even with limited connectivity. Bill your sabji buyers at the mandi gate without waiting for internet. Data syncs automatically when connectivity is restored."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is MandiGrow sabji billing GST compliant?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. MandiGrow generates GST-compliant invoices for sabji trade, supports B2B and B2C billing, and produces ready-to-use data for GSTR-1 and GSTR-3B. Mandi Tax (Cess) for Andhra Pradesh, Telangana, Maharashtra, and Punjab is also supported."}}]}0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","main",null,{"className":"mi